{"expand":"renderedFields,names,schema,transitions,operations,editmeta,changelog","id":"35881","self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/latest/issue/35881","key":"PLXCOMP-29","fields":{"progress":{"progress":0,"total":3600,"percent":0},"summary":"CSharpCompiler does not support the /unsafe[+|-] option to mcs/csc","timetracking":{"originalEstimate":"1h","remainingEstimate":"1h","originalEstimateSeconds":3600,"remainingEstimateSeconds":3600},"issuetype":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issuetype/2","id":"2","description":"A new feature of the product, which has yet to be developed.","iconUrl":"http://jira.codehaus.org/images/icons/issuetypes/newfeature.png","name":"New Feature","subtask":false},"customfield_10110":null,"votes":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/PLXCOMP-29/votes","votes":0,"hasVoted":false},"resolution":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/resolution/1","id":"1","description":"A fix for this issue is checked into the tree and tested.","name":"Fixed"},"fixVersions":[],"resolutiondate":"2006-04-11T12:18:31.162-0500","customfield_10210":"1.0","timespent":null,"reporter":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=cbeams","name":"cbeams","emailAddress":"cbeams@gmail.com","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Chris Beams","active":true},"aggregatetimeoriginalestimate":3600,"customfield_10161":["cbeams(cbeams)"],"customfield_10160":null,"updated":"2007-01-14T13:48:44.758-0600","created":"2006-04-11T12:10:44.270-0500","description":"CSharpCompiler does not have support for the /unsafe option to mcs.  This makes it impossible to compile code that performs unsafe operations.\n\nFollowing convention with the other supported options (target, doc, etc...), the following pom syntax should be supported:\n\n<compilerArguments>\n   <!-- other options -->\n   <unsafe>true</unsafe>\n</compilerArguments>","priority":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/priority/4","iconUrl":"http://jira.codehaus.org/images/icons/priorities/minor.png","name":"Minor","id":"4"},"duedate":null,"issuelinks":[],"customfield_10163":"276480000","watches":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/PLXCOMP-29/watchers","watchCount":0,"isWatching":false},"worklog":{"startAt":0,"maxResults":20,"total":0,"worklogs":[]},"subtasks":[],"status":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/status/5","description":"A resolution has been taken, and it is awaiting verification by reporter. From here issues are either reopened, or are closed.","iconUrl":"http://jira.codehaus.org/images/icons/statuses/resolved.png","name":"Resolved","id":"5"},"customfield_10090":null,"labels":[],"workratio":0,"assignee":null,"attachment":[{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/attachment/20058","id":"20058","filename":"patch.txt","author":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=cbeams","name":"cbeams","emailAddress":"cbeams@gmail.com","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Chris Beams","active":true},"created":"2006-04-11T12:21:30.530-0500","size":1530,"mimeType":"text/plain","content":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/attachment/20058/patch.txt"}],"customfield_10221":null,"customfield_10220":null,"customfield_10200":null,"aggregatetimeestimate":3600,"customfield_10190":null,"project":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/project/11440","id":"11440","key":"PLXCOMP","name":"Plexus Components","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/projectavatar?size=xsmall&pid=11440&avatarId=10011","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/projectavatar?size=small&pid=11440&avatarId=10011","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/projectavatar?size=medium&pid=11440&avatarId=10011","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/projectavatar?pid=11440&avatarId=10011"},"projectCategory":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/projectCategory/10003","id":"10003","description":"various containers","name":"containers"}},"versions":[],"customfield_10170":null,"environment":"General - applies to all","timeestimate":3600,"customfield_10130":null,"aggregateprogress":{"progress":0,"total":3600,"percent":0},"lastViewed":null,"components":[],"comment":{"startAt":0,"maxResults":2,"total":2,"comments":[{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/35881/comment/63327","id":"63327","author":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=cbeams","name":"cbeams","emailAddress":"cbeams@gmail.com","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Chris Beams","active":true},"body":"I've resolved this issue by updating the code for CSharpCompiler.java.  See attachment to follow.\r\n\r\nFor maximum ease of use, three intuitive options are supported for enabling unsafe compilation:\r\n\r\n<compilerArguments>\r\n<unsafe/>\r\n</compilerArguments>\r\n\r\n<compilerArguments>\r\n<unsafe>+</unsafe>\r\n</compilerArguments>\r\n\r\n<compilerArguments>\r\n<unsafe>true</unsafe>\r\n</compilerArguments>\r\n\r\n'false' and '-' are also supported for expressly disabling unsafe compilation (it is disabled by default).\r\n\r\nAny other values supplied will result in a CompilationException being thrown that reads as follows:\r\n\r\n    \"Illegal value [your-value] for <unsafe/>. (must be one of: {'+', '-', 'true', 'false'})\"\r\n\r\nNote: though I have not included a unit test, this code should be simple to review and understand.  It constitued the addition of a single block of code and comments 32 lines long (about 10 lines of actual logic).","updateAuthor":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=cbeams","name":"cbeams","emailAddress":"cbeams@gmail.com","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Chris Beams","active":true},"created":"2006-04-11T12:18:31.150-0500","updated":"2006-04-11T12:18:31.150-0500"},{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/35881/comment/63328","id":"63328","author":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=cbeams","name":"cbeams","emailAddress":"cbeams@gmail.com","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Chris Beams","active":true},"body":"33 line, single block patch adding support for the '/unsafe' compilation option to ./plexus-components/plexus-compiler/plexus-compilers/plexus-compiler-csharp/src/main/java/org/codehaus/plexus/compiler/csharp/CSharpCompiler.java","updateAuthor":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=cbeams","name":"cbeams","emailAddress":"cbeams@gmail.com","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10232","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10232","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10232","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10232"},"displayName":"Chris Beams","active":true},"created":"2006-04-11T12:21:30.569-0500","updated":"2006-04-11T12:21:30.569-0500"}]},"timeoriginalestimate":3600,"aggregatetimespent":null}}